00:36:18,678 --> 00:36:24,016
澳大利亚受致命的壶菌的打击最大
Australia has been hard hit by the deadly fungus, chytrid.

551
00:36:24,084 --> 00:36:26,251
7种两栖动物灭绝了
Seven species have been lost,

552
00:36:26,319 --> 00:36:29,688
更多的物种正在面临相同的命运
And more are on a fast track to extinction.

553
00:36:29,756 --> 00:36:33,459
现在 气候变化 火上加油
Now, add climate change to the mix.

554
00:36:33,526 --> 00:36:37,162
澳大利亚受干旱影响 史无前例
Australia is experiencing its worst drought on record --

555
00:36:37,230 --> 00:36:40,332
两栖动物也受到打击
And amphibians are feeling it.

556
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:42,835
南部的布罗雨滨蛙
In the south, a population of booroolong frogs

557
00:36:42,902 --> 00:36:45,070
在河干时全部死掉了
Was evacuated when their river dried up.

558
00:36:45,138 --> 00:36:50,376
Gerry Marantelli一直养殖青蛙来应对气候变化
Gerry Marantelli has been breeding the frogs to hedge against climate change.

559
00:36:50,443 --> 00:36:52,578
这里有些不错的卵 Erika.
Marantelli: we have some good eggs here, Erika.

